HEADWORD: Instar
<hw>In*star"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To stud as with
stars.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧A golden throne
<xex>instarred</xex> with gems.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>J. Barlow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

