==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Instar
<hw>In"star`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a postembryonic stage
of life of an arthropod, especially an insect, between two successive
molts; also, the arthropod when in that stage of life.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Instate</ent>⟦br⟧
